//annotation of managed_waterbody_type
//model type of hydrology.incubation:ManagedWaterBody named managed_waterbody_type
//observing
//	presence of hydrology.incubation:Reservoir earth:Region named reservoir,
//	presence of hydrology.incubation:Canal earth:Region named managed_canal
//	lookup (reservoir,managed_canal,?) into
//	reservoir|managed_canal|managed_waterbody_type
//	----------------------------------------------
//	   true  | 		#	   |hydrology.incubation:Reservoir,
//		#	 |	   true	   |hydrology.incubation:Canal;